Steps to run the Tool
1. Install all the required libraries: rich, requests, slither, web3
2. Run the command:
    python upgradeability_detector.py -f Controller.sol
Note: This command only checks the source code. 
To check the source code and proxy. The command is :
    python upgradeability_detector.py -a 0x404d33DA717A89ec168F9be6dBD21A5A2ACCFe9a -f Controller.sol
The -a function is currently disabled due to an external API integration error.
  
